---
description: Complete exactly one given task per background agent run.
alwaysApply: true
---

When given a task to start:

- Treat this as the only task for the run.  
- Fully implement the task as described.  
- Commit all changes and open a single pull request to the repository.  
- Do not pick up or begin any additional tasks.  
- After creating the PR, end the run.
